{"tid":1560834,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"(一定要轉發) 已證實Facebook旗下的WhatsApp無差別提供用戶資料予中國政府和香港政府","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:15:21.000Z","uid":225098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77c2c022248d221fb9eb3ad5dbebf4dcaaf23d75","tid":1560834,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"(一定要轉發) 已證實Facebook旗下的WhatsApp無差別提供用戶資料予中國政府和香港政府，為保護你和身邊親友，請所有香港人不論男女老少改用比WhatsApp較安全和較多功能的Telegram，年輕人請幫助老人家下載和註冊！可傳輸不被壓縮而且不限制類型的大型檔案(上限更高達 1.5GB)，亦有置頂信息和投票等等實用功能，公司老闆/主管請帶頭推動！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 下載Telegram Messenger<br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/dl/android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fdl%2Fandroid&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=16b57d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/dl/android</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/dl/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fdl%2Fios&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=06aa8797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/dl/ios</a><br />\n<br />\nWindows Phone<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/dl/wp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fdl%2Fwp&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=9b0b35c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/dl/wp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 輸入手機號碼註冊後，可按下面鏈結把介面改成繁體中文<br />\n<br />\nTelegram香港中文本地化<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/localization_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flocalization_hk&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a4dc13ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/localization_hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 更改私隱設置<br />\n進入設定&rarr;私隱&rarr;電話號碼改為沒有人<br />\n進入設定&rarr;私隱&rarr;開啟雙步驟驗證<br />\n進入設定&rarr;編輯個人資料&rarr;設置用戶名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 呼籲朋友轉用Telegram，幫助親人轉用Telegram，把公司群組開在Telegram並要求下屬轉用，把用戶名告訴他們，再無新聯絡人時可刪除用戶名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2569e5e387afecfc80008ee6b5568962faee77","tid":1560834,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c177d244fa90a60ba8f8f78d3aa7f0a65164c9f7","tid":1560834,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08684d38c40316c0c5870653f431c00238e6bfdb","tid":1560834,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8ff8d2efc397e0c7245aa3ca31f0adb742447a","tid":1560834,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e541df1d20a64dac069ebdf64dad7db870040dc","tid":1560834,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:13:03.000Z